ing%20against%20him.%20In%20one%20newly%20unsealed%20document%2C%20an%20excerpt%20of%20a%20deposition%20given%20by%20Maxwell%2C%20Maxwell%20says%20that%20she%20didn't%20know%20how%20many%20times%20Clinton%20flew%20on%20Epstein's%20private%20jet%20but%20that%20she's%20%26quot%3Bsure%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20a%20meal%20while%20flying%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20also%20bring%20fresh%20scrutiny%20to%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20a%20longtime%20friend%20of%20Epstein%20who%20said%20he%20cut%20ties%20with%20him%20in%202010.%20Another%20Doe%20whose%20name%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20unredacted%20is%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%2C%20one%20of%20Epstein's%20victims%20who%20previously%20said%20the%20prince%20fondled%20her%20at%20his%20Manhattan%20mansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20on%20social%20media%20and%20cable%20news%20have%20speculated%20that%20the%20list%20contains%20a%20comprehensive%20secret%20cache%20of%20the%20dead%20pedophile's%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20descriptions%20of%20their%20lurid%20acts%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20more%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20include%20some%20powerful%20people%20tied%20to%20Epstein.%20But%20the%20list%20also%20includes%20the%20identities%20of%20some%20of%20his%20victims%2C%20household%20staff%2C%20and%20other%20people%20whose%20names%20incidentally%20came%20up%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20long-running%20court%20case%20between%20Virginia%20Roberts%20Giuffre%20and%20Maxwell.%20In%20court%20documents%2C%20these%20people%20were%20previously%20identified%20as%20a%20John%20or%20Jane%20Doe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Does%2C%20for%20example%2C%20previously%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3BJ.%20Doe%20005%26quot%3B%20in%20court%20documents%2C%20is%20Carolyn%20Andriano.%20Andriano%20testified%20against%20Maxwell%20at%20her%20criminal%20trial%2C%20describing%20in%20excruciating%20detail%20how%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-accuser-says-18-was-too-old-for-epste