stein%20settled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvirginia-giuffre-jeffrey-epstein-settlement-doesnt-name-prince-andrew-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20lawsuit%20against%20him%20in%202009%20for%20%24500%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20against%20Maxwell%2C%20brought%20later%2C%20was%20settled%20in%202017%2C%20but%20not%20after%20a%20pitched%20court%20battle%20that%20included%20numerous%20depositions%20and%20a%20discovery%20process%20that%20dredged%20up%20emails%2C%20flight%20manifests%2C%20news%20articles%2C%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-giuffre-v-maxwell-unsealed-thousands-documents-defamation-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecords%20related%20to%20Epstein%2C%20Maxwell%2C%20and%20Giuffre%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20settlement%2C%20the%20civil%20case%20has%20experienced%20a%20long%20afterlife%20as%20various%20parties%20have%20sought%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvirginia-giuffre-lawsuit-led-to-criminal-case-ghislaine-maxwell-epstein-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunseal%20the%20records%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22virginia%20roberts%20giuffre%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f9713f74743a3001216baf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVirginia%20Roberts%20holds%20a%20photo%20of%20herself%20at%20age%2016%2C%20when%20she%20says%20Palm%20Beach%20multimillionaire%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20began%20abusing%20her%20sexually.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Michot%2FMiami%20Herald%2FTribune%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Dershowitz%20has%20sought%20to%20get%20numerous%20filings%20unsealed%2C%20arguing%20they%20would%20disprove%20Giuffre's%20misconduct%20accusations%20against%20him%20as%20well%20(the%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Fdershowitz-accuser-giuffre-drops-defamation-lawsuit-2022-11-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%20a%20large%20number%20of%20lawsuits%20and%20counter-lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20each%20other%20and%20their%20lawyers%20in%202022%2C%20with%20Giuffre%20stating%20she%20%26quot%3Bmay%20have%20made%20a%20mistake%26quot%3B%20saying%20Epstein%20trafficked%20her%20to%20Dershowitz).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Miami%20Herald%20litigated%20to%20unseal%20documents%2C%20some%20of%20which%20were%20used%20for%20its%20explosive%20series%20about%20how%20Epstein%20negotiated%20a%20light%20plea%20deal%20on%20misconduct%20accusations%20around%202007%20with%20prosecutors%20in%20Florida.%20The%20right-wing%20influencer%20and%20conspiracy%20theorist%20Michael%20Cernovich%20also%20hired%20a%20lawyer%20to%20try%20to%20unseal%20documents%20that%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Robert%20Sweet%2C%20who%20originally%20oversaw%20Giuffre's%20lawsuit%20against%20Maxwell%2C%20died%20in%202019%2C%20leaving%20the%20task%20of%20unsealing%20documents%20to%20US%20District%20Judge%20Loretta%20Preska%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20has%20been%20a%20yearslong%20slog.%20Preska%20has%20weighed%20different%20priorities%2C%20including%20the%20public's%20presumption%20of%20access%20to%20court%20documents%20versus%20the%20privacy%20interests%20of%20people%20whose%20names%20have%20come%20up%20in%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20for%20example%2C%20she%20ruled%20that%20Andriano%2C%20Wild%2C%20and%20the%20Farmer%20sisters%20waived%20any%20rights%20to%20privacy%20after%20giving%20media%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20efforts%20to%20unseal%20this%20batch%20of%20records%2C%20Preska%20gave%20the%20Does%20a%20January%201%20deadline%20to%20raise%20any%20new%20objections%20to%20unsealing%20their%20identities.%20Now%20that%20that%20deadline%20has%20passed%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Giuffre%20and%20Maxwell%20have%20been%20ordered%20to%20confer%20and%20then%20publish%20unsealed%20versions%20of%20the%20documents%20on%20the%20court%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Epstein%20Doe%20names%20include%20some%20powerful%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20documents%20in%20the%20Giuffre%20v.%20Maxwell%20lawsuit%20have%20been%20unredacted%20in%20different%20places%20at%20different%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20that%20some%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20be%20as%20benign%20as%20an%20already-public%20Daily%20Mail%20article%20about%20Epstein's%20former%20friend%20Prince%20Andrew%20or%20as%20explosive%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-epstein-questions-dodged-unsealed-deposition-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20Maxwell's%20deposition%20transcripts%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20form%20a%20sort%20of%20puzzle%20where%20journalists%20can%20put%20together%20more%20complete%20versions%20by%20looking%20at%20unredacted%20portions%20in%20different%20places%20on%20the%20court%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20journalists%20have%20been%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20identities%20of%20many%20Does%20even%20before%20they%20were%20officially%20unsealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20%26quot%3BDoe%20183%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20lawyer%20fought%20vociferously%20in%20secret%20court%20filings%20to%20keep%20his%20identity%20under%20wraps%20%E2%80%94%20was%20connected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoe-183-ghislaine-maxwell-jeffrey-epstein-case-sealed-documents-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELes%20Wexner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20billionaire%20former%20L%20Brands%20CEO%20who%20gave%20Epstein%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%201990s%20and%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Wexner%20has%20said%20he%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20Epstein's%20misdeeds%20and%20cut%20off%20ties%20with%20him%20when%20he%20was%20convicted%20of%20soliciting%20girls%20for%20prostitution%20in%202007.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jeffrey%20epstein%20ghislaine%20maxwell%20back%20angle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f0dfdab6f2ebb11f7ceae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican%20financier%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20and%20British%20socialite%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20attend%20a%20birthday%20party%20for%20Michael%20Caine%20at%20The%20Canteen%20restaurant%20in%20Chelsea%2C%20London%2C%2017th%20June%201997.%3Cp%3EDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20Doe%20parties%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20victims.%20In%20a%20previous%20round%20of%20unsealing%2C%20Preska%20disclosed%20that%20two%20of%20them%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjudge-unseals-john-doe-identities-in-ghislaine-maxwell-litigation-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmmy%20Taylor%20and%20Sarah%20Ransome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn't%20make%20sense%20for%20their%20identities%20to%20remain%20private%2C%20Preska%20said%2C%20because%20Taylor%20has%20filed%20lawsuits%20related%20to%20her%20status%20as%20an%20Epstein%20victim%2C%20and%20Ransome%20has%20written%20a%20book%20about%20her%20experience%20being%20trafficked%20by%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20unsealing%20round%20comes%20after%20Preska%20announced%20on%20December%2018%20that%20she%20would%20unseal%20the%20largest%20batch%20yet%2C%20listing%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.447706%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.447706.1315.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%20pages%20of%20Does%3C%2Fa%3E%20going%20up%20to%20%26quot%3BDoe%20187.%26quot%3B%20Since%20the%20identities%20of%20some%20of%20those%20Does%20have%20been%20previously%20made%20public%20%E2%80%94%20