D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthiest%20way%20to%20eat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20they%20also%20identify%20diets%20you%20should%20avoid%20due%20to%20excessive%20restriction%2C%20potential%20side%20effects%2C%20and%20slim%20chances%20of%20long-term%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20raw%20food%20diet%20unhealthy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20raw%20food%20diet%20received%20the%20lowest%20score%20overall%20out%20of%2030%20different%20diets%20based%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20nutritional%20completeness%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20follow%2C%20and%20long-term%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20diet%20includes%20fruit%2C%20raw%20vegetables%2C%20sprouted%20or%20soaked%20raw%20grains%20and%20legumes%2C%20cold-pressed%20olive%20or%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20often%20involves%20lots%20of%20juicing.%20It's%20also%20primarily%20plant-based%20(although%20some%20people%20opt%20to%20include%20raw%20fish%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fheidi-montag-raw-meat-diet-for-fertility-bad-idea-expert-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraw%20meat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20health%20risks).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advocates%20of%20the%20diet%20claim%20that%20raw%20food%20is%20more%20nutritious%2C%20but%20cooking%20some%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%20can%20actually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvegetables-better-cooked-than-raw-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20our%20ability%20to%20absorb%20nutrients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20dietitian%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20downside%20of%20the%20raw%20food%20diet%20is%20that%20it%20eliminates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-enjoy-bread-healthy-diet-according-to-dietitians-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efoods%20that%20can%20be%20healthy%2C%20including%20bread%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prepared%20veggies%2C%20and%20cooked%20beans.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20tricky%20to%20get%20all%20the%20required%20nutrients%20such%20as%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20concern%20about%20the%20raw%20food%20diet%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20very%20low%20in%20calories%20since%20raw%20foods%20are%20typically%20less%20calorie-dense%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20unhealthy%20weight%20loss%20that%20includes%20loss%20of%20muscle%20mass%20or%20bone%20density.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20raw%20food%20diet%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20follow%20long-term%2C%20making%20it%20tough%20to%20dine%20out%20or%20enjoy%20food-related%20social%20events%2C%20according%20to%20the%20expert%20panel.%20Tennis%20superstar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvenus-williams-raw-vegan-diet-what-she-eats-now-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVenus%20Williams%20followed%20a%20raw%20food%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20health%2C%20but%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20wasn't%20sustainable%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20red%20flags%20that%20a%20diet%20is%20unhealthy%20or%20won't%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20raw%20food%20diet%20also%20came%20in%20last%20place%20in%202023%2C%20bumping%20the%20keto%20diet%20from%20the%20bottom%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20experts%20ranked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fketo-low-carb-diet-ranked-worst-healthy-eating-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eketo%20as%20the%20worst%20diet%20to%20follow%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20several%20years.%20The%20low-carb%2C%20high-fat%20plan%20has%20been%20criticized%20for%20potentially%20including%20unhealthy%20processed%20foods%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flazy-keto-diet-easier-to-follow-but-experts-dont-recommend-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20saturated%20fat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20eliminating%20healthy%20foods%20including%20fruit%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20some%20vegetables.%3C