%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Joules%20and%20Watts%3C%2Fa%3E%20coffee%20in%20Malibu%20California%2C%20and%20Jessica%20Rodriguez%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Certified%20Home%20Brewer%20program%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsca.coffee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCA%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20each%20drip%20coffee%20maker%2C%20I%20used%20the%20Peru%20Eufemio%20Dominguez%20Aguilar%20Cajamarca%20from%20Joules%20and%20Watts%20coffee%20roasters%20in%20Malibu%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20considered%20ease%20of%20use%20to%20see%20if%20we%20could%20smoothly%20and%20quickly%20set%20up%20each%20coffee%20maker%2C%20the%20complexity%20of%20cleaning%2C%20and%20whether%20there%20are%20awkward%20controls%20or%20components%20that%20seemed%20likely%20to%20break%20or%20get%20lost.%20For%20machines%20that%20had%20customizable%20brews%2C%20we%20used%20recommended%20presets%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbold%26quot%3B%20settings%20to%20determine%20if%20the%20cup%20was%20over%20or%20under%20extracted.%20Since%20taste%20is%20subjective%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20consistent%20results%20above%20all%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20different%20coffee%20makers%20on%20a%20counter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6331d86b329bac00182f3887%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDylan%20Ettinger%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20drip%20coffee%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20coffee%20can%20work%20in%20a%20coffee%20maker%2C%20but%20make%20sure%20your%20coffee%20is%20fresh.%20Most%20roasters%20print%20the%20roast%20date%20on%20every%20bag%20of%20coffee.%20Try%20to%20find%20a%20coffee%20roasted%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20before%20you%20want%20to%20brew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20if%20you%20can%2C%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-coffee-grinder%5C%22%3Ebest%20coffee%20grinder%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20grind%20your%20coffee%20just%20before%20brewing.%20%26quot%3BOptimally%2C%20freshly%20roasted%20and%20freshly%20ground%20coffee%20goes%20into%20the%20coffee%20maker.%20Yes%2C%20grinding%20is%20an%20extra%20step%20and%20yes%2C%20it%20is%20completely%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaultieri%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20fresh%20grounds%20in%20coffee%20makers%20really%20make%20a%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways!%26quot%3B%20Gaultieri%20says.%20After%20roasting%2C%20all%20of%20the%20flavorful%20oils%20and%20sugars%20start%20to%20decay%20and%20the%20gasses%20inside%20the%20coffee%20beans%20leak%20out%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20dull%20and%20stale%20flavor.%20Pre-grinding%20your%20coffee%20long%20before%20brewing%20amplifies%20that%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20coffee%20starts%20to%20lose%20volatile%20aromatic%20compounds%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20is%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gaultieri.%20By%20breaking%20up%20the%20beans%20and%20releasing%20more%20of%20the%20gasses%20and%20exposing%20the%20organic%20compounds%20and%20oils%20to%20the%20air%2C%20it%20spoils%20even%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20coffee%20blooming%20and%20why%20is%20it%20important%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBlooming%2C%20or%20pre-infusing%2C%20is%20when%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20hot%20water%20is%20used%20to%20soak%20the%20beans%20in%20order%20to%20help%20release%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20gas%20in%20the%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20blooming%2C%20the%20CO2%20bubbles%20released%20can%20disrupt%20the%20overall%20brewing%20process%20by%20making%20the%20ground%20bed%20uneven%20and%20leading%20to%20uneven%20extraction.%20Many%20coffee%20makers%20now%20utilize%20a%20programmed%20pre-infusion%20process%20to%20help%20create%20a%20more%20evenly%20extracted%20and%20full-flavored%20cup%20of%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20should%20I%20buy%20an%20electric%20coffee%20maker%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20coffee%20makers%20excel%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20consistency.%20%26quot%3BA%20coffee%20machine%20is%20programmed%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20every%20time%20it%20is%20turned%20on%2C%20and%20if%20it%20is%20a%20good%20machine%2C%20it%20will%20do%20this%20very%20consistently%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rodriguez.%20Electric%20coffee%20makers%20also%20often%20have%20features%20such%20as%20timed%20brewing%2C%20which%20can%20save%20time%20in%20the%20morning%20if%20your%20schedule%20is%20tight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20filters%20should%20I%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20are%20reusable%20metal%20or%20mesh%20filters%20and%20single-use%20paper%20filters.%20Some%20makers%20even%20allow%20the%20user%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20difference%20between%20filtration%20types%20is%20how%20much%20of%20the%20dissolved%20coffee%20solids%20and%20oils%20they%20allow%20to%20pass%20through.%20%26quot%3BFiltration%20affects%20the%20beverage%20clarity%20which%20affects%20the%20body%2Fmouthfeel%20sensory%20experience%20of%20coffee%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodriguez%20says.%20Reusable%20filters%20have%20the%20added%20bonus%20of%20producing%20less%20waste%20and%20cutting%20long-term%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20sets%20an%20SCA-certified%20home%20brewer%20apart%20from%20other%20coffee%20makers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Specialty%20Coffee%20Association%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsca.coffee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20a%20program%20that%20rigorously%20tests%20coffee%20makers%20and%20certifies%20the%20ones%20that%20perform%20to%20their%20standards.%20Any%20SCA-certified%20brewer%20is%20proven%20to%20produce%20high-quality%2C%20consistent%20cups%20of%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Jessica%20Rodriguez%2C%20Certifications%20Program%20Manager%20at%20the%20SCA%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3BMultiple%20production%20units%20are%20submitted%20and%20tested%20at%201L%20and%20full%20capacity%20for%20adequate%20brew%20basket%20space%20to%20hold%20the%20SCA%20Golden%20Cup%20ratio%20of%2055g%2FL%2C%20that%20they%20can%20reach%20and%20maintain%20a%20brewing%20temperature%20of%2092%20%E2%80%93%2096C%2C%20the%20total%20water%20contact%20time%20falls%20between%204%20%E2%80%93%208%20minutes%2C%20the%20total%20dissolved%20solids%20of%20each%20brew%20falls%20between%201.15%25%20-%201.45%25%20and%20is%20consistent%20from%20extraction%20to%20extraction%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20good%20beverage%20clarity.%20Submitted%20brewers%20are%20also%20subjected%20to%20a%20uniformity-of-extraction%20test%20procedure%20that%20analyzes%20the%20spent%20coffee%20bed%20for%20the%20evenness%20of%20extraction.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-coffee-maker%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704318784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6543f4f6b788914e554f23b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-coffee-maker%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20coffee%20makers%20fit%20your%20routine%20and%20brew%20style%2C%20plus%20have%20steady%20temperature%20control.%20Here%20are%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20espresso%2C%20single-serve%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ettingerdylan%40gmail.com%20(Dylan%20Ettinger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A201%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-coffee-maker%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpaceX%20Illegally%20Fired%208%20Workers%20Who%20Criticized%20Elon%20Musk%3A%20