per%20cent%20profit.%20A%20liquor%20lobby%20it%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Group%26quot%3B%20had%20paid%20kickbacks%2C%20part%20of%20which%20was%20routed%20to%20public%20servants.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20alleged%20laundering%20of%20the%20kickbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam%20were%20used%20by%20the%20AAP%20to%20fund%20its%20large-scale%20campaign%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20in%20which%20it%20got%20a%2012.91%20per%20cent%20votes%20and%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20national%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20saying%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bshaking%20in%20fear%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20not%20appearing%20before%20the%20agency%20because%20he%20knows%20that%20he%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bkingpin%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704310260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fuqkq1ae8_arvind-kejriwal-ndtv-file-photo_625x300_03_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-be-arrested-today-aap-leaders-raise-alarm-4795407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20could%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20have%20tweeted.%20Party%20sources%20said%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20any%20eventuality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-be-arrested-today-aap-leaders-raise-alarm-4795407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-be-arrested-today-aap-leaders-raise-alarm-4795407%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-be-arrested-today-aap-leaders-raise-alarm-4795407%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20%E2%80%98May%20December%E2%80%99%20a%20Comedy%3F%20%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704309300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FM230919_ZX006.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C152px%252C3000px%252C1688px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235860085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20few%20years%2C%20the%20Golden%20Globe%20awards%20have%20a%20category%20hiccup.%20In%202015%2C%20the%20Ridley%20Scott%2FMatt%20Damon%20Robinson-Crusoe-in-space%20sci-fi%20movie%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Martian%E2%80%9D%20was%20nominated%20(and%20won)%20for%20best%20motion%20picture%20%E2%80%94%20musical%20or%20comedy%2C%20even%20though%20the%20movie%20contained%20no%20songs%20and%20no%20one%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20comedy.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20in%20that%20same%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Owen%20Gleiberman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fmay-december-comedy-camp-todd-haynes-julianne-moore-natalie-portman-1235860085%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fmay-december-comedy-camp-todd-haynes-julianne-moore-natalie-portman-1235860085%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fmay-december-comedy-camp-todd-haynes-julianne-moore-natalie-portman-1235860085%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Portal%20Saw%2016%20Lakh%20Cyberattacks%20A%20Minute%20During%20Summit%20In%20Sept%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cybersecurity%20sector%20repelled%20numerous%20cyberattack%20attempts%20on%20the%20G20%20portal%20during%20the%20summit%20and%2016%20lakh%20DDoS%20attacks%20per%20minute%20peaked%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Cybercrime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%20CEO%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20made%20the%20revelation%20during%20the%20annual%20conference.%20The%20I4C%20wing%2C%20which%20was%20established%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20a%20framework%20and%20eco-system%20for%20Law%20Enforcement%20Agencies%20(LEAs)%20to%20deal%20with%20cybercrime%20in%20a%20coordinated%20and%20comprehensive%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20query%2C%20Kumar%20said%20per%20minute%2C%2016%20lakh%20attacks%20were%20noted%20on%20the%20G20%20account%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20and%20it%20started%20soon%20after%20the%20website%20was%20up%20and%20the%20attacks%20peaked%20during%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20clarified%20that%20the%20I4C%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20multiple%20Indian%20agencies%20concerned%2C%20managed%20to%20thwart%20these%20attacks%20and%20keep%20the%20website%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20raised%20concerns%20about%20some%20non-national%20foreign%20threat%20actors%20operating%20through%20the%20Virtual%20Private%20Network%20(VPN)%2C%20showing%20their%20attempts%20from%20China%2C%20Cambodia%20and%20Malaysia.%20But%20he%20said%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20say%20the%20exact%20place%2C%20as%20VPN%20networks%20disguise%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20hacker's%20real%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20cyber%20experts%2C%20non-national%20threat%20actors%20send%20Distributed%20Denial%20of%20Service%20(DDoS)%20to%20disrupt%20and%20try%20to%20sabotage%20any%20site.%20These%20attacks%20could%20have%20originated%20from%20foreign%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20summit%20was%20the%20eighteenth%20meeting%20of%20the%20G20.%20It%20was%20held%20in%20Delhi's%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20International%20Exhibition-Convention%20Centre%20on%20September%209-10%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20conference%2C%20Kumar%20also%20said%20more%20than%2031%20lakh%20cybercrime%20complaints%20have%20been%20registered%20so%20far%20on%20the%20National%20Cybercrime%20Reporting%20Portal%20(ww