%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20identified%20as%20Pramod%2C%20was%20rushed%20to%20four%20different%20government%20hospitals%20by%20the%20police%20personnel%20due%20to%20the%20unavailability%20of%20beds%20or%20equipment%20at%20the%20hospitals%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20failure%20to%20get%20admission%20at%20any%20hospital%20resulted%20in%20his%20death%20at%205.45%20am%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatrolling%20staff%20was%20taking%20the%20accused%20to%20the%20New%20Usmanpur%20police%20station%20after%20he%20had%20molested%20and%20abused%20a%20woman%20near%20Shanti%20Mohalla.%20The%20accused%20was%20in%20an%20inebriated%20condition%20and%20was%20vomiting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%2C%20northeast%2C%20Joy%20Tirkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20suddenly%20jumped%20off%20the%20moving%20vehicle%20after%20opening%20the%20glass%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20further%20said%20that%20he%20fell%20on%20the%20road%20and%20was%20immediately%20taken%20to%20the%20Jag%20Pravesh%20Chandra%20(JPC)%20Hospital%20from%20where%20he%20was%20referred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injured%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20GTB%20Hospital%20by%20an%20ambulance%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20be%20admitted%20there%20because%20of%20the%20unavailability%20of%20CT-Scan.%20He%20was%20referred%20to%20LNJP%20hospital%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20be%20admitted%20there%20due%20to%20unavailability%20of%20beds%20in%20the%20ICU%20Ventilator%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tirkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injured%20was%20later%20rushed%20to%20the%20RML%20Hospital%2C%20but%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20denied%20admission.%20He%20was%20again%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20JPC%20Hospital%2C%20where%20the%20injured%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%205.45%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20said%20that%20a%20medical%20board%20is%20being%20constituted%20to%20conduct%20an%20autopsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20details%20of%20the%20incident%20in%20which%20Pramod%20was%20taken%20into%20police%20custody%2C%20Tirkey%20said%20that%20the%20police%20control%20room%20received%20a%20call%20around%209%20pm%20from%20a%20woman%20living%20in%20Shanti%20Mohalla%20in%20New%20Usmanpur%2C%20alleging%20that%20she%20was%20abused%20and%20molested%20by%20a%20drunk%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20a%20police%20team%20was%20sent%20and%20the%2021-year-old%20complainant%20told%20them%20that%20Pramod%20was%20drunk%20and%20molested%20her.%20When%20the%20woman%20stopped%20him%2C%20he%20started%20quarrelling%20with%20her%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20team%20arrested%20Pramod%20from%20the%20spot%20and%20was%20bundled%20into%20the%20police%20van%20to%20take%20him%20to%20the%20New%20Usmanpur%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20jumped%20as%20the%20police%20van%20reached%20near%20the%20police%20station.%20It's%20strange%20that%20no%20hospital%20could%20give%20him%20proper%20medical%20treatment.%20The%20patient%20kept%20on%20hopping%20from%20hospital%20to%20hospital%20to%20hospital.%20We%20have%20started%20further%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20DCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20of%20molestation%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20assault%20was%20later%20registered%20at%20the%20police%20station%20on%20the%20woman's%20complaint%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20further%20said%20Pramod%20was%20found%20previously%20involved%20in%20two%20criminal%20cases%2C%20including%20that%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20my%20notice%20by%20media%20query%20that%20a%20victim%20of%20road%20accident%20was%20allegedly%20refused%20admission%20by%20three%20Delhi%20government%20hospi