ed%20in%20the%20petitions%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20cabal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20revels%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20thing%20and%20I%20am%20sorry%20to%20say%20that%20some%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20they%20take%20up%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20are%20not%20in%20national%20interest.%20That%20is%20the%20best%20that%20can%20be%20said%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jethmalani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20predecessor%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20the%20one%20on%20Rafale%2C%20which%20also%20met%20with%20failure%20in%20the%20top%20court%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bsame%20lawyers%2C%20same%20petition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20even%20te%20review%20petition%20for%20Rafale%20got%20dismised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20keeps%20happening.%20The%20same%20bunch%20of%20people%2C%20acting%20at%20the%20interest%20of%20foreign%20powers%20inimical%20to%20India's%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20a%20%26quot%3Bword%20of%20caution%26quot%3B%20--%20saying%20every%20time%20such%20petitions%20are%20brought%2C%20it%20would%20get%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704302940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fl1d9tps8_mahesh-jethmalani-_625x300_23_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-hindenburg-verdict-mahesh-jethmalani-alleges-cabal-in-supreme-court-4794932%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20has%20alleged%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bcabal%26quot%3B%20is%20operating%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bringing%20politically%20motivated%20petitions%2C%20%26quot%3Bacting%20at%20the%20interest%20of%20foreign%20powers%20inimical%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%