-year-old%20domestic%20help%20was%20bitten%20by%20a%20German%20Shepherd%20breed%20dog%20while%20she%20was%20waiting%20in%20the%20gallery%20of%20the%2018th%20floor%20of%20Tower%20B%20of%20the%20society%20where%20she%20worked%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20door%20of%20the%20neighbouring%20apartment%20was%20ajar%20and%20the%20dog%20came%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20pouncing%20on%20the%20domestic%20help%20and%20leaving%20her%20severely%20injured%20before%20the%20pet-owner%20gained%20control%20on%20the%20canine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20similar%20incident%20had%20happened%20two%20months%20ago%20with%20a%20maintenance%20staffer%20of%20the%20society%20by%20the%20same%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complainant%20claimed%2C%20urging%20the%20police%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20action%26quot%3B%20under%20a%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20case%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20German%20Shepherd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20pet%20owner%20%26quot%3Bintimidated%26quot%3B%20the%20domestic%20help%20against%20filing%20a%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisrakh%20police%20station%20in-charge%20Inspector%20Arvind%20Kumar%20said%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20against%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20289%20(negligent%20conduct%20with%20respect%20to%20animals)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20provocation%20to%20breach%20peace)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20underway%20and%20while%20the%20offence%20is%20bailable%20it%20could%20attract%20a%20prison%20term%20or%20fine%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndi