even%20years%20and%20got%20bail%20only%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20Gurugram's%20Sector%2014%20police%20station%20said%20they%20received%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20family%20of%2027-year-old%20Divya%20Pahuja%20that%20she%20had%20gone%20out%20with%20her%20friend%20Abhijeet%20Singh%20on%20January%201%20and%20had%20gone%20missing.%20They%20informed%20the%20police%20that%20Singh%20owned%20Hotel%20City%20Point%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20that%20Pahuja's%20phone%20had%20been%20switched%20off%20for%20several%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20police%20reached%20the%20hotel%20and%20checked%20the%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20they%20saw%20a%20body%20wrapped%20in%20a%20sheet%20being%20dragged%20down%20a%20corridor.%20Singh%20and%20two%20of%20his%20aides%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20former%20model's%20murder%20and%20police%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20find%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20Singh%20had%20allegedly%20paid%20the%20two%20men%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20put%20the%20body%20in%20his%20BMW%20and%20dump%20it%20somewhere%20it%20would%20not%20be%20found.%20The%20two%20aides%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Omprakash%20and%20Hemraj%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Drove%20In%20Direction%20Of%20Punjab'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20official%20said%20Pahuja%20had%20gone%20out%20with%20Singh%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%20and%20they%20had%20reached%20his%20hotel%2C%20along%20with%20one%20of%20Singh's%20associates%2C%20around%204.15%20am%20the%20next%20day.%20They%20were%20joined%20by%20at%20least%20one%20other%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20they%20killed%20Pahuja%2C%20two%20of%20Singh's%20aides%20dragged%20the%20body%20down%20the%20hotel%20corridor%20and%20put%20it%20in%20his%20BMW.%20They%20drove%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Punjab%20and%20disposed%20of%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGangster%20Connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPahuj