20Amor%20Cash%2C%20GuayabaCash%2C%20EasyCredit%2C%20Cashwow%2C%20CrediBus%2C%20FlashLoan%2C%20PrestamosCredito%2C%20Prestamos%20De%20Credito-YumiCash%2C%20Go%20Credito%2C%20Instantaneo%20Prestamo%2C%20Cartera%20grande%2C%20Rapido%20Credito%2C%20Finupp%20Lending%2C%204S%20Cash%2C%20TrueNaira%20and%20EasyCash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20who%20discover%20any%20of%20the%20above-mentioned%20apps%20on%20their%20phones%20should%20delete%20them%20immediately%20and%20change%20passwords%20for%20their%20devices%2C%20financial%20accounts%20and%20Wi-Fi%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%20They%20should%20also%20be%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20symptoms%20of%20a%20potential%20malware%20infection%2C%20including%20suspicious%20alerts%20and%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704290340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F46domarg_smartphone-generic_650x400_24_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsmartphone-users-warned-to-delete-dangerous-apps-check-list-4793917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20experts%20have%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20smartphone%20users%20to%20delete%20some%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%26quot%3B%20financial%20apps%20from%20their%20phones%20as%20they%20have%20been%20found%20to%20be%20infected%20with%20malware.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsmartphone-users-warned-to-delete-dangerous-apps-check-list-4793917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsmartphone-users-warned-to-delete-dangerous-apps-check-list-4793917%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsmartphone-users-warned-to-delete-dangerous-apps-check-list-4793917%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMore%20Than%20Vindication%26quot%3B%3A%20Harish%20Salve%20On%20Supreme%20Court's%20Hindenburg%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20backing%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchanges%20Board%20of%20India%20or%20SEBI%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20has%20made%20a%20comeback%2C%20veteran%20lawyer%20Harish%20Salve%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Attorney%20General%20also%20said%20the%20other%20high%20point%20of%20the%20judgment%20is%20the%20underscoring%20of%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%20which%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20will%20help%20democracy%20flourish.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20democracy%20cannot%20survive%20if%20these%20two%20vital%20principles%20are%20sidestepped%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20this%20evening%2C%20Mr%20Salve%2C%20who%20has%20represented%20India%20many%20times%20in%20international%20courts%2C%20said%20the%20judgment%20is%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20just%20a%20vindication%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20restores%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salve%20said%2C%20citing%20how%20in%20the%20years%20after%202014%2C%20there%20was%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20distrust%20in%20the%20country%20following%20allegations%20of%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20of%20law%20became%20a%20casualty.%20The%20principle%20of%20separation%20of%20powers%20was%20breached%20when%20courts%20started%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20regulatory%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20declaring%20that%20took%20nine%20years%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20constitutional%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20judgment%20today%2C%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20allegations%20of%20OCCRP%20-%20an%20organisation%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%20and%20others%20-%20can't%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20doubting%20SEBI's%20investigation%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20has%20investigated%2022%20out%20of%20the%2024%20cases%20linked%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20petitioners'%20appeal%20for%20the%20case%20to%20be%20transferred%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20said%20the%20power%20to%20transfer%20investigation%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20exercised%20in%20exceptional%20circumstances%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20powers%20cannot%20be%20exercised%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20cogent%20justifications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20remarking%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20justify%20such%20a%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20has%20been%20given%20three%20months%20to%20complete%20investigation%20in%20the%20remaining%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20supreme%26quot%3B%20and%20under%20it%2C%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20can%20only%20be%20treated%20as%20inputs%20and%20not%20evidence%2C%20by%20the%20regulatory%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salve%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704290040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj5s6bbn_hairsh-salve-ndtv-interview_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmore-than-vindication-harish-salve-on-supreme-courts-hindenburg-order-4793903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20backing%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchanges%20Board%20of%20India%20or%20SEBI%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20has%20made%20a%20comeback%2C%20veteran%20lawyer%20Harish%20Salve%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht