80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F260%2FAU1639.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%5C%22%3Eofficial%20records%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthrilled%20to%20share%20that%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20has%20welcomed%20three%20new%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20post%20on%20January%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20roaring%20success%20for%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20envisioned%20by%20PM%20Shri%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%5C%22%3E%20%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20to%20restore%20ecological%20balance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPurrs%20in%20the%20wild!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrilled%20to%20share%20that%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20has%20welcomed%20three%20new%20members.%20The%20cubs%20have%20been%20born%20to%20Namibian%20Cheetah%20Aasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20roaring%20success%20for%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20envisioned%20by%20PM%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20to%20restore%20ecological%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20big%20congrats%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fc1fXvVJN4C%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fc1fXvVJN4C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20(%40byadavbjp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbyadavbjp%2Fstatus%2F1742493594693607625%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20mention%20when%20the%20cubs%20were%20born%2C%20though%20the%20video%20shows%20that%20all%20three%20cubs%20have%20opened%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcheetah.org%2Flearn%2Fabout-cheetahs%2F%5C%22%3ECheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20director%20Laurie%20Marker%20was%20involved%20in%20translocating%20some%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20to%20India%2C%20cheetah%20cubs%20usually%20weigh%208.5%20to%2015%20ounces%20(around%20240%20grams%20to%20425%20grams)%20at%20birth%20%E2%80%9Cand%20are%20blind%20and%20helpless%E2%80%9D.%20As%20per%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fielc.libguides.com%2Fsdzg%2Ffactsheets%2Fcheetah%2Freproduction%5C%22%3Eestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cubs%20open%20their%20eyes%20between%20four%20to%2011%20days%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESecond%20litter%20in%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20litter%20of%20African%20cheetah%20cubs%20to%20be%20born%20in%20the%20country%20since%20the%20ambitious%20Project%20Cheetah%20was%20launched%2C%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20eight%20cheetahs%20from%20Namibia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20March%20this%20year%2C%20cheetah%20Jwala%20(earlier%20called%20Siyaya)%20%E2%80%93%20also%20brought%20from%20Namibia%2C%20just%20like%20Aasha%20%E2%80%93%20gave%20birth%20to%20four%20cubs%2C%20more%20than%2070%20years%20after%20cheetahs%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20land%20mammal%2C%20were%20declared%20officially%20extinct%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20three%20of%20the%20four%20cubs%20born%20to%20Jwala%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20died%20on%20May%2023%2C%202023%2C%20as%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cweak%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20runt%20of%20the%20litter%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Forest%20Department%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcheetah-cub-dies-in-kuno%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20press%20note.%20The%20press%20note%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20survival%20rate%20of%20cheetah%20cubs%20in%20Africa%20is%20very%20low%20and%20as%20per%20experts%20and%20available%20literature%2C%20their%20survival%20rate%20in%20open%20forests%20is%20only%2010%25.%20Under%20natural%20circumstances%2C%20only%20one%20in%2010%20cheetah%20cubs%20attain%20adulthood%2C%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20on%20May%2025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Ftwo-more-cheetah-cubs-die-in-kuno%5C%22%3Etwo%20more%20cubs%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20dehydration%2C%20per%20forest%20authorities.%20Authorities%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20two%20cubs%E2%80%99%20death%20could%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20extreme%20heat%20(the%20temperature%20in%20Kuno%20was%2046-47%C2%B0C%20then)%20and%20the%20dry%20summer%20wind%2C%20which%20worsened%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F260%2FAU1639.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20August%20last%20year%20that%20the%20cubs%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cheat%20stress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704287193000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03183404%2Fimage-1682.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetah-cubs-born-on-indian-soil%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20cubs%20have%20been%20born%20to%20Aasha%2C%20a%20cheetah%20brought%20from%20Namibia%20in%20September%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetah-cubs-born-on-indian-soil%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twinkle%20Khanna's%20Maldives%20Vacation%20Is%20The%20Best%20Way%20To%20Start%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20and%20columnist%2C%20Twinkle%20Khanna%20is%20currently%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fswirlster.ndtv.com%2Ftravel%2Fbefore-her-shah-rukh-khan-movie-