%2C%20as%20per%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Ftravel%2Fnews%2F2023%2F06%2F27%2Froyal-caribbeans-icon-of-the-seas-largest-cruise-ship%2F70362440007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20are%20positioning%20it%20as%20the%20ultimate%20family%20vacation%2C%20and%20when%20you%20step%20back%20and%20look%20at%20all%20the%20energy%20and%20time%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20creating%20this%20ship%20it%20is%20mind-blowing%2C''%20Mr%20Bayley%20said%20in%20an%20earlier%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%20of%20the%20Cruise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2Ficon-of-the-seas-royal-caribbean%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Royal%20Caribbean%20International's%20'Icon%20of%20the%20Seas'%20is%20365%20meters%20long%20and%20weighs%20a%20projected%20250%2C800%20tonnes.%C2%A0It%20can%20hold%20about%205%2C610%20passengers%20and%202%2C350%20crew%20members%20and%20cost%20%242%20billion%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20luxurious%20cruise%20boasts%2020%20decks%2C%20a%20food%20hall%2C%20and%20six%20pools%2C%20and%20will%20offer%20vacationers%20the%20world's%20largest%20waterpark%20at%20sea%2C%20dubbed%20Category%206.%C2%A0''It's%20thrilling%20you%20never%20dared%20to%20imagine%20and%20next-level%20chill%20you%20never%20dreamed%20possible.%20Let%20your%20adrenaline%20surge%20at%20the%20largest%20waterpark%20at%20sea%20or%20conquer%20an%20all-out%20test%20of%20courage%20dangling%20high%20above%20the%20ocean%2C''%20Royal%20Caribbean%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20offer%20a%20resort%20getaway%2C%20a%20beach%20escape%2C%20a%20theme%20park%2C%20and%20over%20%26quot%3B40%20ways%20to%20dine%2C%20drink%2C%20and%20be%20entertained%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20Guests%20who%20want%20a%20more%20leisurely%20experience%20can%20also%20relax%20in%20the%20boat's%20seven%20pools%20and%20nine%20whirlpools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20attractions%20include%20an%20aqua%20park%20for%20families%2C%20a%20swim-up%20bar%2C%20exclusive%20dining%20experiences%2C%20arcades%2C%20live%20music%2C%20and%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704284580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F739ut9s8_icon-of-the-seas_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficon-of-the-seas-worlds-largest-cruise-ship-spotted-in-puerto-rico-ahead-of-debut-see-pics-4793293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cruise%20is%20scheduled%20to%20welcome%20the%20public%20for%20its%20first%20commercial%20voyage%20on%20January%2027.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficon-of-the-seas-worlds-largest-cruise-ship-spotted-in-puerto-rico-ahead-of-debut-see-pics-4793293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficon-of-the-seas-worlds-largest-cruise-ship-spotted-in-puerto-rico-ahead-of-debut-see-pics-4793293%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficon-of-the-seas-worlds-largest-cruise-ship-spotted-in-puerto-rico-ahead-of-debut-see-pics-4793293%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'At%20least%2070%20killed'%20in%20explosions%20near%20tomb%20of%20Iranian%20Guards%20commander%20during%20ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704284460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-iran-blast-explosion_6411136.jpg%3F20240103134138%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-least-20-killed-in-explosions-near-tomb-of-iranian-guards-commander-qassem-soleimani-during-ceremony-13041479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20explosion%20at%20a%20cemetery%20in%20Iran%20where%20a%20ceremony%20was%20being%20held%20to%20mark%20the%202020%20assassination%20o