i-group-hindenburg%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20transfer%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20from%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20to%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT).%20The%20court%20said%20that%20SEBI%20had%20concluded%20its%20investigation%20in%2022%20out%20of%20the%2024%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20held%20that%20there%20were%20no%20valid%20grounds%20raised%20to%20direct%20SEBI%20to%20revoke%20its%20amendments%20on%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPI)%20and%20Listing%20Obligations%20and%20Disclosure%20Requirements%20(LODR)%20regulations.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20regulations%20do%20not%20suffer%20from%20any%20infirmities%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-adani-group-hindenburg%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20also%20dismissed%20the%20reliance%20on%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20report%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Creliance%20on%20a%20third%20party%20organisation%20report%20without%20any%20verification%20cannot%20be%20relied%20upon%20as%20a%20proof.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReliance%20on%20newspaper%20reports%20and%20third%20party%20organisations%20to%20question%20the%20statutory%20regulator%20does%20not%20inspire%20confidence.%20They%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20inputs%20but%20not%20conclusive%20evidence%20to%20doubt%20SEBI%20probe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20had%20initially%20ordered%20SEBI%20to%20submit%20its%20findings%20by%20August%2014%2C%202023.%20It%20had%20later%20asked%20the%20regulator%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20November%208%2C%202023.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20it%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20complete%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20pending%20two%20cases%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3E%20released%20a%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20accusing%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20fraud%2C%20including%20the%20manipulation%20of%20stock%20prices%20to%20artificially%20inflate%20their%20value.%20The%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdani%20is%20pulling%20the%20largest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2FInvetsors%2FAdani-Response-to-Hindenburg-January-29-2023.pdf%5C%22%3Erefuted%20these%20allegations%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20dismissing%20the%20report%20as%20a%20tactic%20by%20foreign%20entities%20to%20undermine%20India%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20publication%20of%20the%20report%20study%20stirred%20controversy%20in%20the%20political%20circles%2C%20prompting%20a%20closer%20examination%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20Gautam%20Adani.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20uproar%2C%20political%20leaders%20and%20activists%20filed%20several%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PILs)%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwith-hindenburg-adani-faces-his-stiffest-challenge-yet%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20short%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20instead%20focussed%20on%20its%20international%20bonds.%20In%20an%20analytical%20piece%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20delved%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20extensive%20expansion%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20not%20only%20in%20sectors%20where%20it%20was%20already%20present%2C%20but%20also%20in%20newer%20sectors%20like%20airports%2C%20renewables%2C%20cement%2C%20defence%2C%20data%20centres%2C%20agriculture%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3Erelease%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2024%2C%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20covered%20all%20events%20related%20to%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20matter.%20Here%20are%20some%20reports%20that%20provide%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20significant%20developments%20since%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%E2%80%99s%20publication%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fgautam-adanis-brother-behind-undisclosed-pledging-of-adani-shares-to-russian-bank-for-loan-forbes%5C%22%3EGautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20Brother%20Behind%20Undisclosed%20Pledging%20of%20Adani%20Shares%20to%20Russian%20Bank%20for%20Loan%3A%20Forbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20(February%2017%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Adani%2C%20the%20elder%20brother%20of%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20gained%20prominence%20following%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20expanding%20Adani%20Group%20firms%2C%20with%20an%20alleged%20web%20of%20companies%20in%20various%20offshore%20territories%20that%20have%20apparently%20not%20been%20disclosed%20to%20regulatory%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Shantilal%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20also%20published%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0wrote%20about%20a%20previously%20undisclosed%20role%20of%20Singapore-based%20Pinnacle%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Pte.%20Lte%2C%20which%20was%20%E2%80%9Cindirectly%20controlled%E2%80%9D%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20in%20allegedly%20pledging%20Adani%20Group%20promoter%20stocks%20for%20a%20loan%20from%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20VTB%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claimed%20that%20Pinnacle%20had%20entered%20into%20a%20loan%20arrangement%20with%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20VTB%20bank%20in%202020.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20April%202021%2C%20Pinnacle%20had%20borrowed%20%24263%20million%20and%20lent%20out%20%24258%20million%20to%20an%20unnamed%20related%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Singaporean%20filings%2C%20Pinnacle%20offered%20two%20investment%20funds%20as%20guarantors%20for%20the%20loan%20from%20the%20Russian%20state-owned%20bank.%20These%20investment%20funds%20were%20identified%20as%20Afro%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Investments%20Limited%20and%20Worldwide%20Emerging%20Market%20Holding%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0articles%20linked%20two%20Indian%20stock%20exchange%20filings%20in%20June%202020%20and%20August%202022%2C%20showing%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cultimate%20beneficial%20owner%20of%20Mauritius-based%20Acropolis%20Trade%20and%20Investments%20Limited%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20owns%20100%25%20of%20Worldwide%20Emerging%20Market%20Holding%20Limited%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20claimed%20that%20Afro%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Worldwide%20hold%20%244%20billion%20worth%20of%20promoter%20stock%20in%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20Adani%20Transmission%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Adani%20Power.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0also%20noted%20that%20as%20per%20the%20investment%20tracking%20website%20Trendlyne%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrendlyne.com%2Fportfolio%2Fsuperstar-shareholders%2Fcustom%2F%3Fquery%3Dafro%2520asia%2520trade%2520and%2520investments%2520limited%5C%22%3EAfro%20Asia%20Trade%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrendlyne.com%2Fportfolio%2Fsuperstar-shareholders%2Fcustom%2F%3Fquery%3Dworldwide%2520emerging%2520market%2520holding%2520limited%5C%22%3EWorldwide%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20not%20hold%20any%20other%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbecause-of-repealed-provisions-sebi-hit-opaque-structure-wall-while-investigating-adani-sc-panel%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBecause%20of%20Repealed%20Provisions%2C%20SEBI%20Hit%20%E2%80%98Opaque%20Structure%E2%80%99%20Wall%20While%20Investigating%20Adani%3A%20SC%20Panel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cstrong%3EMay%2019%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20constituted%20a%20five-member%20an%20expert%20committee%20to%20probe%20any%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20Adani%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20A.M.%20Sapre%2C%20had%20as%20its%20members%20former%20SBI%20chairman%20O.P.%20Bhatt%2C%20Justice%20J.P.%20Devadhar%20(retired)%2C%20veteran%20banker%20K.V.%20Kamath%2C%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Nandan%20Nilekani%20and%20advocate%20Somasekhar%20Sundaresan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%20the%20expert%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fanalysing-the-adani-debacle%5C%22%3Ereleased%20its%20report%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20concluding%20that%20SEBI%20hit%20an%20%E2%80%98opaque%20structure%20wall%E2%80%99%20while%20investigating%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%9Copaque%20structure%E2%80%9D%20in%20this%20context%20points%20to%20FPIs%20located%20in%20offshore%20countries.%20The%20opacity%20of%20these%20structures%20arises%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20ultimate%20beneficiaries%20or%20owners%20are%20not%20transparent%20or%20easily%20discernible.%20The%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20such%20financial%20arrangements%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20ascertain%20the%20true%20ownership%20or%20control%20of%20the%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20because%20%E2%80%9Cin%202018%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20dealing%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98opaque%20structure%E2%80%99%20and%20requiring%20an%20FPI%20to%20disclose%20every%20ultimate%20natural%20person%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20chain%20of%20every%20owner%20of%20economic%20interest%20with%20the%20FPI%20was%20done%20away%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20SEBI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sebi.gov.in%2Fsebi_data%2Fattachdocs%2Fjan-2019%2F1546513057420.pdf%5C%22%3Esubstituted%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20words%C2%A0%E2%80%98beneficial%20ownership%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98common%C2%A0ownership%20or%20control%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FPI%20situation%20raised%20questions%20on%20Adani%20Group%20companies%E2%80%99%20free%20float%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublicly%20traded%20companies%20are%20required%20to%20have%20at%20least%2025%25%20of%20their%20shares%20held%20by%20non-promoters%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20retail%20investors%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20FPIs%2C%20and%20insurance%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20to%20stay%20listed%20on%20exchanges.%20These%20shares%20are%20called%20public%20float%20or%20free%20float%20or%20public%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-vinod-adani-free-float-rules%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20data%20from%20Trendlyne%2C%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Adani%20Group%2C%20a%20few%20investment%20funds%20hold%20most%20of%20the%20free%20float.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20FPIs%2C%20whose%20details%20are%20not%20available%20online%2C%20keeps%20on%20increasing%20year%20on%20year.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20Andy%20Mukherjee%20called%20these%20FPIs%20%E2%80%9CAdani%E2%80%99s%20fortune%20drivers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20role%20gained%20attention%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%98he%20and%20Adani%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20one%E2%80%99.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20can%20be%20assumed%20he%20also%20has%20influence%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20management%2C%20although%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20managerial%20position%20in%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-raises-related-party-concerns-over-adani-ports-deals-with-3-entities%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeloitte%20Resigns%20Because%20It%20Was%20Not%20Given%20a%20%E2%80%9CWider%20Audit%20Role%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cstrong%3EMay%2031%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20media%20reports%20highlighted%20concerns%20related%20to%20the%20auditors%20involved%20in%20assessing%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20financial%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%202%2C%202023%2C%20barely%20a%20year%20after%20its%20reappointment%2C%20Shah%20Dhandharia%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20an%20Ahme%C2%ADdabad-based%20chartered%20accountancy%20firm%2C%20resigned%20as%20statutory%20auditor%20of%20Adani%20Total%20Gas.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20independent%20auditor%20for%20Adani%20Enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20noted%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctiny%20firm%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Cseems%20to%20have%20no%20current%20website.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20audit%20partners%20at%20Shah%20Dhandharia%20who%20respectively%20signed%20off%20on%20Adani%20Enterprises%20and%20Adani%20Total%20Gas%E2%80%99%20annual%20audits%20were%20as%20young%20as%2024%20and%2023%20years%20old%20when%20they%20began%20approving%20the%20audits.%20They%20were%20essentially%20fresh%20out%20of%20school%2C%20hardly%20in%20a%20position%20to%20scrutinise%20and%20hold%20to%20account%20the%20financials%20of%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20companies%20in%20the%20country%2C%20run%20by%20one%20of%20its%20most%20powerful%20individuals%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemorningcontext.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhow-the-adani-group-worked-its-way-around-a-forensic-audit%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EMorning%20Context%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20October%202022%20report%2C%20Shah%20Dhandharia%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20and%20Dharmesh%20Parikh%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20that%20audit%20most%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20have%20links%20to%20each%20other%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20raise%20concerns%20over%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20paid%20them%20a%20little%20over%20Rs%207%20crore%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Rs%2084%20crore%20paid%20by%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2031%2C%20Deloitte%20raised%20concerns%20over%20Adani%20Ports%E2%80%99%20transactions%20with%20three%20entities%2C%20which%20the%20company%20said%20were%20unrelated%20parties.%20However%2C%20the%20auditor%20said%20it%20could%20not%20confirm%20that%20the%20parties%20were%20indeed%20unrelated.%20It%20has%20also%20issued%20a%20qualified%20opinion%20on%20the%20accounts%20of%20Adani%20Ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20statutory%20auditors%20of%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20(APSEZ).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeloitte%E2%80%99s%20note%20said%20that%20the%20company%20has%20also%20refused%20to%20get%20an%20independent%20external%20examination%20that%20would%20help%20prove%20so.%20This%20is%20because%20SEBI%20is%20investigating%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%20against%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeloitte%2C%20therefore%2C%20said%20that%20it%20cannot%20comment%20if%20the%20company%20was%20fully%20compliant%20with%20local%20laws%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-05-31%2Fdeloitte-flags-adani-port-transactions-citing-lack-of-review%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%2Fcid%2F1958682%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETelegraph%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20APSEZ%20said%20Deloitte%20had%20resigned%20because%20it%20was%20not%20given%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwider%20audit%20role%E2%80%9D%20covering%20other%20listed%20Adani%20portfolio%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20in%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-12%2Fadani-contractor-probed-by-india-resurfaces-under-a-new-name%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20maintains%20ties%20with%20the%20controversial%20contracting%20firm%2C%20Howe%20Engineering%20Projects%20(India)%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20Taiwanese%20family%2C%20raising%20governance%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-contractor-probed-by-india-resurfaces-under-a-new-name-11702362098726.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20contracting%20firm%20contains%20the%20core%20operations%20of%20a%20business%20called%20PMC%20Projects%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPMC%20Projects%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20firms%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsecond-inflated-imports-case-adani-struck%5C%22%3Ewas%20accused%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20inflating%20the%20value%20of%20imported%20power%20and%20infrastructure%20goods%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20nearly%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20alleged%20that%20the%20firm%20was%20being%20used%20by%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20empire%20to%20siphon%20money%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%20and%20the%20probe%E2%80%99s%20findings%20were%20dismissed%20in%202017%20by%20the%20adjudicating%20authority%20of%20DRI%2C%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-dismisses-plea-claiming-overvaluation-in-imported-goods-by-adani-123032800508_1.html%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20all%20the%20imports%20were%20genuine.%20It%20concluded%20that%20the%20value%20declared%20was%20correct%20and%20was%20not%20required%20to%20be%20re-determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Deloitte%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20determine%20whether%20Howe%20should%20be%20labelled%20a%20related%20party%20was%20why%20the%20auditor%20raised%20red%20flags%20about%20payments%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20ports%20company%20to%20the%20contracting%20firm%20in%20May%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20Research%20directly%20called%20out%20PMC%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20an%20Adani%20related%20party%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20suck%20money%20out%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20publicly%20listed%20entities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-concealed-dri-letter-on-stock-market-manipulation-by-adani-group-in-2014-petitioner-to-sc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESEBI%20%E2%80%98Concealed%E2%80%99%20DRI%20Letter%20on%20Stock%20Market%20Manipulation%20by%20Adani%20Group%20in%202014%3A%20Petitioner%20to%20SC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cstrong%3ESeptember%2012%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20found%20that%20the%20markets%20regulator%20had%20known%20about%20the%20stock%20manipulation%20allegations%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055231%2Fsebi-knew-about-allegations-against-adani-group-since-2014-letter-shows%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20filed%20an%20affidavit%2C%20accusing%20SEBI%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconcealing%E2%80%9D%20an%20alert%20it%20received%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20in%20January%202014%20about%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20claimed%20the%20DRI%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20then%20SEBI%20chairperson%2C%20U.K.%20Sinha%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%202014%2C%20alerting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20may%20be%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20companies%20using%20the%20money%20siphoned%20off%20through%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20power%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20DRI%20had%20sent%20a%20CD%2C%20containing%20evidence%20of%20siphoning%20of%20Rs%202%2C323%20crore%20and%20notes%20on%20the%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20anti-smuggling%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OCCRP%20report%20was%20also%20shared%20with%3Cem%3E%C2%A0The%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Sinha%2C%20the%20then%20SEBI%20head%2C%20currently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fndtv-appoints-former-sebi-chairman-uk-sinha-as-non-executive-chairman-16279441.htm%5C%22%3Eserves%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20the%20non-executive%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3EOverpricing%20of%20Coal%20Imports%20by%20Adani%20Group%20Led%20to%20Higher%20Profits%2C%20Customers%20Overcharged%20for%20Fuel%3A%20FT%3C%2Fa%3E%20(October%2012%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20a%20detailed%20investigation%2C%20titled%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20mystery%20of%20the%20Adani%20coal%20imports%20that%20quietly%20doubled%20in%20value%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Adani%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20coal%20importer%2C%20has%20been%20inflating%20fuel%20costs%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmillions%20of%20Indian%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20overpaying%20for%20electricity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20described%20Adani%20as%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99s%20Rockefeller%E2%80%99%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20sharply%20rising%20fortunes%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpegasus-used-to-target-the-wires-founding-editor-reporter-working-on-adani-amnesty-confirms%5C%22%3EPegasus%20Used%20to%20Target%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20Founding%20Editor%2C%20Reporter%20Working%20On%20Adani%2C%20Amnesty%20Confirms%3C%2Fa%3E%20(December%2028%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F2023.12.28-021126%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F27%2Findia-apple-iphone-hacking%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Erevealed%2C%20citing%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%2C%20that%20it%20has%20detected%20evidence%20that%20Pegasus%20spyware%20was%20used%20by%20an%20unknown%20government%20agency%20to%20compromise%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20two%20journalists%20in%20India%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Anand%20Mangnale%20of%20the%20Oraganised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project.%20The%20%3Cem%3EPost%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Aug.%2023%2C%20the%20OCCRP%20emailed%20Adani%20seeking%20comment%20for%20a%20story%20it%20would%20publish%20a%20week%20later%20alleging%20that%20his%20brother%20was%20partof%20a%20group%20that%20had%20secretly%20traded%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20public%20stock%2C%20possibly%20in%20violation%20of%20Indian%20securities%20law.%20A%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20conducted%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20shared%20withThe%20Washington%20Post%2C%20found%20that%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%2C%20the%20notorious%20spyware%C2%A0that%20was%20developed%20by%20Israeli%20company%20NSO%20Groupand%20that%20NSO%20says%20is%20sold%20only%20to%20governments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20said%20its%20Security%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20observed%20indications%20of%20renewed%20Pegasus%20spyware%20threats%20towards%20individuals%20in%20India%20during%20a%20regular%20technical%20monitoring%20exercise%20in%20June%202023%2C%20a%20number%20of%20months%20after%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20seeking%20to%20procure%20a%20new%20commercial%20spyware%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple%20issued%20threat%20notifications%20globally%20to%20iPhone%20users%20who%20may%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%2C%20Varadarajan%2C%20Mangnale%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20journalists%20and%20opposition%20politicians%20in%20India%20received%20the%20notifications.%20Among%20those%20who%20went%20public%20at%20the%20time%20were%20Mahua%20Moitra%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Nair%2C%20a%20journalist%20with%20OCCRP%20who%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Adani%20story%20with%20Mangnale.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704281412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16194940%2Fadanis.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-vinod-adani-to-pegasus-targeting-on-reporter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20listicle%20detailing%20some%20significant%20developments%20since%20Hindenburg%20Research%20released%20its%20report%2C%20accusing%20the%