0a%20powerful%20signalling%20value%20and%20cost%20across%20India.%20It%E2%80%99s%20part%20of%20a%20bottom-up%20organic%20force%20that%20legitimises%20resistance%20against%20any%20government%20that%20fails%20to%20take%20groups%20into%20consultation%20for%20laws%2Fexecutive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContext%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20craft%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fonline-views%2Fno-political-arena-should-look-like-a-football-stadium-11577896100534.html%5C%22%3Eexplained%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20right%20after%20CAA-NRC%20protests%20had%20taken%20the%20nation%20by%20storm%2C%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%20of%20Beliefs%3C%2Fem%3E%20economist%20and%20philosopher%20Kaushik%20Basu%20argued%20how%20in%20context%20of%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20those%20founded%20on%20principles%20of%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20two%20elements%20are%20most%20critical%20in%20the%20legislative%20process%20for%20upholding%20and%20safeguarding%20constitutional%20values%3A%20An%20efficient%20administration%20and%20a%20dignified%20process%20of%20governance.%20An%20inability%20to%20ensure%20one%20would%20naturally%20affect%20the%20other.%20In%20theory%2C%20all%20this%20can%20make%20sense%20in%20a%20country%20where%20governance%20is%20aligned%20with%20principles%20of%20constitutional%20and%20civic-institutional%20morality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20if%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20case%20in%20actuality%20(as%20we%20see%20in%20the%20current%20context).%20What%20if%20a%20state%20decides%20to%20create%20laws%20for%20implementation%20that%20involve%20the%20creation%20of%20targets%20and%20polarise%20society%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20bulldozing%20has%20coercively%20institutionalised%20a%20process%20of%20non-consultative%20law-making%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20create%20targets%2C%20or%20polarised%20outcomes%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20reflects%20a%20disdain%20for%20basic%20constitutional%20morals%20and%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fonline-views%2Fno-political-arena-should-look-like-a-football-stadium-11577896100534.html%5C%22%3ECAA-NRC-NPR%20combination%3C%2Fa%3E%20allowed%20for%20creating%20targets%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%2C%20and%20it%20went%20along%20with%20a%20state%20narrative%20to%20allow%20the%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20legitimatisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20legalised%20political%20project%20of%20pitting%20one%20group%20in%20opposition%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20instance%20in%20this%20regard%20were%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fin-photos-remembering-the-farmers-protest-a-triumph-of-satyagraha-politics%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKaale%20Kanoon%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Black%20Farm%20Laws)%E2%80%9D%20brought%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20divided%20farmers%2C%20and%20even%20those%20advocating%20for%20agri-reforms%2C%20leading%20to%20one%20of%20the%20largest%2C%20longest%20peaceful%20protest%20movements%20in%20contemporary%20India%20(and%20the%20world).%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fin-photos-remembering-the-farmers-protest-a-triumph-of-satyagraha-politics%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKisan%20Andolan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20the%20government%20bend%20on%20its%20knees%20and%20take%20the%20legislations%20back%2C%20which%20were%20also%20railroaded%20without%20any%20consciously%20expanded%20deliberation%2C%20or%20consultative%20process%20with%20farmers%20unions%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatyagraha%20protest%20politics%3A%20An%3Cem%3E%20andolan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20learn%20from%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplugging%20back%20to%20the%20lessons%20emerging%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fin-photos-remembering-the-farmers-pro