n%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Railways.%20An%20Amravati-based%20social%20activist%2C%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20had%20filed%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20queries%20with%20five%20of%20those%20zones%20%E2%80%93%20Central%20Railways%2C%20Western%2C%20Southern%2C%20Northern%2C%20and%20North%20Western%20Railways%20%E2%80%93%20asking%20for%20details%20on%20costs%20associated%20with%20the%20selfie%20booths.%20The%20Central%20Railways%20was%20the%20only%20zone%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20query%20on%20specific%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20Central%20Railway%20Zone%20alone%2C%20around%2020%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20each%2C%20totalling%20to%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%20There%20are%20another%2032%20odd%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20(a%20total%20of%20Rs%2040%20lakh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20from%20CR%20was%20supplied%20by%20deputy%20GM%20Abhay%20Mishra%2C%20but%20the%20CPRO%20has%20been%20shunted%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bose%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaspure%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Swapnil%20D.%20Nila%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20change.%20Other%20officials%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctop-level%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20stations%20are%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20places%20where%20the%20government%20is%20using%20taxpayer%20money%20to%20put%20up%20these%20Modi%20selfie%20points.%20Universities%2C%20public%20areas%2C%20etc.%20too%20have%20seen%20these%20selfie%20points%20spring%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704266454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentral-railways-pro-transferred-without-notice-after-releasing-costs-of-modi-selfie-points%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Railways%20was%20the%20only%20zone%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20RTI%20query%20on%20specific%20costs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentral-railways-pro-transferred-without-notice-after-releasing-costs-of-modi-selfie-points%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'Last%20Press%20Conference%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM%20in%20India'%20Was%2010%20Years%20Ago%20on%20This%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03114623%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Journalist%20Pankaj%20Pachauri%20has%20pointed%20out%20on%20X%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20press%20conference%E2%80%9D%20by%20an%20Indian%20prime%20minister%2C%20was%20held%20exactly%20a%20decade%20ago%20on%20this%20day%2C%20January%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20last%20press%20conference%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM%20was%20held%20exactly%2010%20years%20ago%20today.%2062%20unscripted%20questions%20answered%20with%20100%2B%20journalists%20present%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20presser%20mentioned%20by%20Pachauri%2C%20then%20prime%20minister%20Dr.%20Manmohan%20Singh%20hosted%20over%20100%20journalists%20who%20asked%20him%20over%2062%20questions.%20Pachauri%20was%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20information%20and%20communications%20advisor.%20In%20his%20time%20in%20office%2C%20Singh%20was%20often%20criticised%20by%20the%20now-ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20his%20silence%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20press%20conference%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM%20was%20held%20exactly%2010%20years%20ago%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E62%20unscripted%20questions%20answered%20with%20100%2B%20journalists%20present.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fkxm4o2Wyc0%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fkxm4o2Wyc0%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FR7vfBHNzWg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FR7vfBHNzWg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Pankaj%20Pachauri%20(%40PankajPachauri)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPankajPachauri%2Fstatus%2F1742385858534383814%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPachauri%20probably%20meant%20that%20this%20was%20the%20last%20press%20conference%20by%20an%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20in%20India%2C%20because%20despite%20his%20refusal%20to%20conduct%20pressers%2C%20current%20prime%20minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20answered%20two%20questions%20by%20journalists%20in%20the%20White%20House%20during%20his%202023%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20has%20not%20appeared%20in%20a%20single%20press%20conference%20in%20India%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-us-media-covered-modis-reception-by-biden-amidst-criticism-on-human-rights%5C%22%3EThe%20White%20House%20episode%20was%20so%20rare%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThough%20he%20loves%20speeches%20at%20public%20events%2C%20and%20has%20leaned%20into%20his%20monthly%20radio%20show%20as%20a%20way%20to%20deliver%20messages%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20any%20exposure%20to%20unscripted%20events%20had%20been%20a%20rarity%20before%20the%20White%20House%20event%2C%20and%20probably%20will%20be%20again%20afterward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20before%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchivepmo.nic.in%2Fdrmanmohansingh%2Fspee